{"tid":2002903,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)霸吧 爸爸霸 霸吧 爸爸霸 霸吧 霸爸4-6","createTime":"2020-05-05T12:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T18:56:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad4f97b4a80ec2b42924e05c9e46881d6dac9e5","tid":2002903,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=d58fb21a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=43b0ff83\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=2e8be41e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xT9DPpf0zTqRASyzTi/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxT9DPpf0zTqRASyzTi%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c76575e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VMLiPi9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVMLiPi9.jpg&h=bd706e0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.銀河系中，內戰不斷，莉亞公主攜帶著偷取的帝國的終極武器&mdash;&mdash;死星的藍圖，乘坐一艘外交使船前往反抗軍基地，但途中被黑武士率兵截獲。緊急情況下，莉亞公主將藍圖和求救信息藏在R2-D2中，R2-D2和C-3PO乘坐一艘逃生艙前往塔圖因，尋求絕地大師歐比王&middot;肯諾比的幫助。在塔圖因上，R2-D2和C-3PO被原住民爪哇族（Jawa）抓獲，隨後被賣給了路克&middot;天行者的叔叔歐文&middot;拉爾斯<br />\n<br />\n2.黑武士一心專注於找到路克&middot;天行者和反抗軍同盟的基地，因此派出大量的偵察機器人，遍布整個星系展開搜索，最終在冰球霍斯(Hoth)探測到了回音基地的存在，黑武士隨即集結了大批帝國風暴兵準備進攻霍斯。<br />\n而在此之前，路克觀測到「隕石」（實則為帝國的偵察機器人）的出現，正要進一步調查時，卻遭遇了雪地怪獸丸帕（Wampa）並被抓到其洞中。路克利用原力成功逃生，但最後在冰天雪地中迷失了方向<br />\n<br />\n3.為了救出處於碳冷凍狀態的韓&middot;索羅，莉亞&middot;歐嘉納、藍道&middot;卡利森和丘巴卡經過策畫，分別以不同方法潛入赫特人賈霸的根據地。偽裝成賞金獵人的莉亞雖然成功解除碳冷凍設定，喚醒了韓，卻也同時掉入賈霸設下的陷阱，被賈霸抓去當成自己貼身專用的女奴，韓則被關入牢內<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=305eff16\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=866785ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcceb4b0b52c95d99e0f083ce35e27d957986244","tid":2002903,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T12:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse